-ADDA-471C-AD1F-3F5CF1A0A0B9-1536x856.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/B1C66622-ADDA-471C-AD1F-3F5CF1A0A0B9-2048x1141.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/B1C66622-ADDA-471C-AD1F-3F5CF1A0A0B9.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Exoprimal》是一款線上團隊對戰動作遊戲，故事設定在未來的 2043 年。時空漩渦因未知原因頻繁開啟，向現代世界釋放出無盡的恐龍群，這現象被稱為「恐龍爆發」。為對抗這群遠古巨獸，艾比奧斯公司開發出新世代 AI「利維坦」，它能預測恐龍爆發即將發生的地點。艾比奧斯公司還開發出最新型動力裝甲服「強攻裝甲（Exosuits）」，用以武裝英勇的「攻裝戰士（Exofighters）」來對抗恐龍侵襲。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090159" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-694x386.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-694x386.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-1280x713.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-768x428.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-1536x855.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C-2048x1140.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/448C7FE2-D017-4EA9-A2BA-A3C23982BF4C.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-1280x708.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-1536x849.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E-2048x1132.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/46A1C4F1-E20E-41B0-BCAA-6CC529FDA49E.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-1280x708.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-1536x849.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC-2048x1132.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/38D953AC-5A94-4510-AFA1-CA002BEFACFC.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-694x386.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-694x386.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-1280x712.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-768x427.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-1536x855.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D-2048x1139.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/A765AEFF-381A-4864-BA38-B5AAB8C1FD2D.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-694x383.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="383" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-694x383.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-1280x707.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-768x424.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-1536x848.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD-2048x1131.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08DA6927-9748-4356-B604-011D3D4CD5CD.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在遊戲中，玩家可選擇「前鋒」、「護盾」與「支援」三種不同類型的強攻裝甲，以五人小隊連線的方式與對戰隊伍競爭，並打敗發起侵襲的大批恐龍，包括暴龍、迅勐龍與羽齒龍等熟悉恐龍的大軍狂潮。目前已確定有擅長遠距輸出的「神射手」、講究走位的「疾風」、高耐久坦克「路障」以及治療隊友的「巫醫」此 4 尊攻裝戰士可使用。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Exoprimal》存在不同任務類型，以主要模式「恐龍生存戰」為例，比對戰隊伍更快完成 AI 「利維坦」提出的任務就獲得勝利，任務詳情會根據玩家經驗與技術提供不同情境。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090164" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-694x425.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-694x425.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-1280x783.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-768x470.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-1536x940.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86-2048x1253.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/E4CE4BD6-D22F-499B-97E3-F752D6C58A86.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Exoprimal》將於 2023 年推出，登上 PS4/PS5、Xbox One/Xbox Series X/S 和 Steam。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_11641"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tndjXQkA5mY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來：<a href="https://youtu.be/tndjXQkA5mY">YouTube</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
