4" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44-1280x709.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44-1536x851.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44-2048x1134.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/CD1BB270-51E7-42EF-8C45-AC2D71339C44.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">隨著「女武神」開啟故事篇章，遊戲將逐步描繪「人類的死亡」和「諸神的存在」。《Valkyrie Elysium》預計 2022 年內發售，將登陸 PS4、PS5 以及 Steam。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_13610"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x19cl1Wiyfg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來：<a href="https://youtu.be/x19cl1Wiyfg">YouTube</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
